goaU5Fjdojjr41w&fr=pb","date":"2010-05-17 12:58","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":26,"title":"回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Image\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%CA%D7%C1%EC%D0%A1%B5%B0%B5%B0/pic/item/05676edce73718c576c638c0.jpg\" width=\"264\" changedsize=\"false\">","author":"☆银色的风铃★","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a80b337b.cBMMQgmCHUj91GoYnWB1WQ?t=1536762349&fr=pb","date":"2010-07-18 20:07","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/__tangtian__/pic/item/6b0d45ed59ee980e63d09f98.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":27,"title":"回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"8好意思，偶坑了这么久的文……","author":"☆银色的风铃★","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a80b337b.cBMMQgmCHUj91GoYnWB1WQ?t=1536762349&fr=pb","date":"2010-09-20 19:21","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/__tangtian__/pic/item/6b0d45ed59ee980e63d09f98.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":28,"title":"回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"接下来，开始华丽丽的发文喽！（好吧，我承认我的文并不怎么华丽……）<br>——————————————————————————---<br>突然地回头，GIGI看到了正在微笑的王子，那一瞬间，王子的身上仿佛发出无限的光芒，耀眼的可以灼伤别人的眼眸！一抹红晕，浮上了她的脸。<br>“你是王子吗？”GIGI小心的问着，如同崇拜自己的信仰般。<br>“嗯，我叫上官帅。你可以叫我上官哦！”王子的脸上，笑容在隐去，取而代之的是淡淡的，无法抹去的忧伤。看着她的模样，有一种陌生的熟悉感。<br>“我叫GIGI！”她微笑着，似乎愿意用自己的微笑去抚平王子的忧伤。<br>王子温柔的揉了揉她的发丝，这个熟悉的动作，似乎很久没有做过了。<br>夜晚，GIGI睡在放在王子的房间的蔷薇花上。<br>梦，有些幻美，却难以捉摸，那些梦境那么熟悉，却又那么陌生！脑海里的一些情节，正在回放。却有些情节，如同玻璃的碎片，零零碎碎，永远无法拼凑完整。是支离破碎的记忆吗？还是只是单纯的梦境……<br>“已愿意和我一起去学校吗？”<br>“什么，我和你一起去吗？”她高兴的睁大了眼睛，忽闪忽闪的。<br>“对啊！”<br>“好啊，好啊！”她高兴的拍起手来。<br>说完后，ＧＩＧＩ才发现，自己好像少了一点少女的矜持啊！似乎还笑的好花痴呢。<br>“呵呵。”王子有些尴尬的笑。<br>“那么，我把你放进我的书包喽，会很小心的保护你哦！”<br>“呵呵。”ＧＩＧＩ似乎有些害羞，红晕抹在了脸颊上。她的脑中，有一些碎片在拼凑以来，那一句“会很小心的保护你哦”好像很熟悉啊，是不是有人对自己说过的吗？<br>不容她多想，就已经被王子轻轻捧起，放进了书包，那个空间很大，似乎是王子特意为ＧＩＧＩ空出来的空间。还将书包的拉链拉开，好让它呼吸。王子真是一个很相信的人呢！<br>想到这儿，她甜蜜的笑了。<br>———————————————————————————————————<br>今天先写这么多！（偶素冰河蓝雅！）\u0018","author":"☆银色的风铃★","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a80b337b.cBMMQgmCHUj91GoYnWB1WQ?t=1536762349&fr=pb","date":"2010-09-20 19:59","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/__tangtian__/pic/item/6b0d45ed59ee980e63d09f98.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":31,"title":"回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Image\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%CA%D7%C1%EC%D0%A1%B5%B0%B5%B0/pic/item/05676edce73718c576c638c0.jpg\" width=\"264\" changedsize=\"false\">","author":"伊十王道","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.221e46ed.k6MSPSQTG5zGwrCgOVLuBg?t=1417776031&fr=pb","date":"2010-09-26 21:18","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":33,"title":"回复：回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"文文写的很好，希望尽快更文","author":"吻手背","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5daeb27d.xmI2PQU7bc35DAiYijmGZg&fr=pb","date":"2011-10-13 12:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":34,"title":"回复：回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Image\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%CA%D7%C1%EC%D0%A1%B5%B0%B5%B0/pic/item/05676edce73718c576c638c0.jpg\" width=\"264\" changedsize=\"false\"><img class=\"BDE_Image\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%CA%D7%C1%EC%D0%A1%B5%B0%B5%B0/pic/item/05676edce73718c576c638c0.jpg\" width=\"264\" changedsize=\"false\">\u0018","author":"轩爱TAN深爱","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2bf8a390.Xg0wERwnux_p8dx1Z-y6Tw&fr=pb","date":"2012-01-28 14:34","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":35,"title":"回复：回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0006.gif\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\">","author":"吻手背","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.5daeb27d.xmI2PQU7bc35DAiYijmGZg&fr=pb","date":"2012-01-28 17:17","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":36,"title":"回复：回复：【帅GI】蔷薇恋人","content":"<img class=\"BDE_Image\" src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%CA%D7%C1%EC%D0%A1%B5%B0%B5%B0/pic/item/05676edce73718c576c638c0.jpg\" width=\"264\" height=\"385\